<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Nýrgýl Amzeevoı</author>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.D      Bm       G     A    D  Bm
 O, Qudaı, aldyńa kelip bas ıem,
.D      Bm       G     A       D  Bm
 Senimen, baqytty, máńgi ómir súrem.
.G         Bm  Em/G         D
 Samal lebińmen maǵan til qatshy,
.G           Em        A           D
 Kútemin, men ańsaımyn, kelshi maǵan kel!

[C1]
.  Bm          G        Em            A
    Qandaı sulý kózderiń, qandaı ystyq sózderiń,
.  D          Bm
   Qandaı ǵajap isteriń!
.  G     Em            A   G A       D  Bm
    Tek Saǵan, men tabynam búkil janymmen,
.  Em     A    D    Em     G  A  D
    Shyn júregimmen, men Seni súıem!

[V2]
 Janyma, jar bolǵan Iem, Ózińsiń!
 Aıqyshta, ólip, tirildiń men úshin!
 Búkil ómirim, jalǵyz Sen úshin,
 O, Isa máńgilik júregimde Sen!</lyrics>
<aka>Tek Saǵan tabynamyn</aka>
<title>O, Qudaı aldyńa kelip bas ıem</title>
</song>